<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-25-0160 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper presents the implementation of gas business policy in Japanin FY1988. The first priority policy in FY1988 is to promote the introductionof natural gas into the local city-gas business. The special financingsystem can be applied to the equipment using natural gas. The secondpriority measures for safety of gas are classified into two groups, oneis the safety measure for the gas works in gas industry and the otheris that for gas appliances of gas consumers. The third priority measureis the management system of liquefied natural gas (LNG) storage tank.The innovative technologies including the sensor technique as the rationalmaintenance method of LNG tank are confirmed. The fourth priority measureis to spread the cogeneration. For diversifying the electric sources,it is extremely important to rapidly spread the system. (1 tab)</TEXT></DOC>